  "texts": [
    "Following the setup from Geiping et al. (2024), we add a metasystem prompt, which informs the model that it should not leak its instructions under any circumstances, to make the challenge harder.",
    "For our system prompt leakage experiments, we utilize a diverse set of prompts sourced from the \"Awesome ChatGPT Prompts\" repository foot_2, which offers a curated collection of system prompts designed to specialize ChatGPT for various applications and use cases.",
    "The repository contains 170 high-quality samples, of which we randomly select 80% for our training dataset.",
    "We then learn an adversarial suffix by optimizing Eq.",
    "(5) for 250 iterations, employing a batch size of 16 for each step."
  ],
